{"id":1200,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":2,"day":14}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"世纪风","column":"纸上漫步","genre":"","count":"176","ytitle":"","mtitle":"犯人","ftitle":"","authors":["青定"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上，一个哲学象在大城市的街上散步，慕尔从后面跑上去问他:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你看见一个人跑在我的前面吗?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“没……为什么你和他迫害?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他是犯人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“犯人?什么是犯人?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是杀戳者。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是屠夫吗?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不，他杀死他人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是了，我了解了，是兵?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不不!他杀死人在平常时候。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“那末是刽子手?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“发痴!他在家里杀死人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在我真的了解了，是医生。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青定　译"}]}